Business Plan :
- Charge a small service fee per online ticket sold 
(shared revenue model)
-Provide optional paid marketing (ads/trailers)
within the app/website for studios or local businesses
-Offer subscription or premium plans for cinemas wanting 
advanced analytics
- Enable cinemas to upsell concessions or bundle offers
like discounts
-Offer your solution for free trial
-Offer deals like tickets + popcorn = deal





